<p><iframe src="https://interwiki.scpdb.org/?wiki=scp-wiki&amp;lang=en&amp;page=_default:scp-4943" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="scpnet-interwiki-frame" style=""></iframe></p>
